Rippleitt does not control, and does not accept any responsibility or liability for, the privacy policy of, and use of personal information by, any party other than Rippleitt.


Third-party vendors, including Google, may show ads on sites across the Internet.  The Rippleitt App makes use of the Google Maps API to assist with location based information. More information about the Google Maps API and the related privacy policy can be found here http://www.google.com/privacy.html


